{"tid":2181948,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【I/A】守望傳說 Guardian Tales (23) 養生等狐狸bb","createTime":"2020-08-31T03:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T04:36:53.000Z","uid":283244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a68204c27f09a3846fbf59f6e78a48c4d621074b","tid":2181948,"uid":283244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>廠商：Kakao Games Corp.含中資</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kakaogamescorp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kakaogamescorp.com%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=db4e8ad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kakaogamescorp.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM0S7Gn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM0S7Gn.jpg&h=a7a96c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://esportsobserver.com/kakao-games-raises-130-million/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fesportsobserver.com%2Fkakao-games-raises-130-million%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=0e5baa21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://esportsobserver.com/kakao-games-raises-130-million/</a><br />\nKakao Games, the gaming division of South Korean messaging giant Kakao, raised around 140 billion won ($130 million) from a number of investors, led by Tencent. The Chinese megacorp invested 50 billion won ($47 million) in Kakao Games, now owns 22 percent<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4BrddG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4BrddG.png&h=9a125772&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yElhPIu9oyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyElhPIu9oyc&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=160aa54c\" target=\"_blank\">https://